                                        Digitalization - thinking inside of the box
				








By 2020, online sales in the U.S. are projected to reach $523 billion annually.  When a package arrives at your doorstep, there's a box, inside a box, inside a box.  To meet demand, companies like Cascades are investing in state-of-the-art technology such as Greenpac in Niagara Falls, NY.











