                                Drilling – offshore and onshore
                                














Drilling – offshore and onshore  



Energy exploration is an industry where machine reliability is crucial, because if your machinery stops drilling, your profits suffer.
Many of the world’s leading offshore and onshore drilling companies trust Mobil™ industrial lubricants to help extend the service life of machine components and reduce oil changes.
Mobil Serv℠ Engineering Services also provides expert technical advice and solutions to help keep your energy exploration equipment running longer and more efficiently, all while also reducing costs and environmental impact. We do this by proactively: 

Analyzing and optimizing lubricant performance
Troubleshooting equipment issues
Inspecting and monitoring equipment

With Mobil industrial lubricants, you’ve got a partner that has a profound understanding of your business, even at some of the most remote locations. We’re here to help you explore which products and services can help you reach your business objectives.


